level-up.name: take-down
level-up.description:
A reckless, full-body charge attack for slamming into
the target. This also damages the user a little.
level-up.effect: Inflicts regular damage.  User takes 1/4 the damage it inflicts in recoil.

tutor.name: iron-defense
tutor.description:
The user hardens its body’s surface like iron,
sharply raising its Defense stat.
tutor.effect: Raises the user's Defense by two stages.

tutor.name: zen-headbutt
tutor.description:
The user focuses its willpower to its head and
attacks the target. This may also make the
target flinch.
tutor.effect: Inflicts regular damage.  Has a 20% chance to make the target flinch.

tutor.name: iron-head
tutor.description:
The user slams the target with its steel-hard head.
This may also make the target flinch.
tutor.effect: Inflicts regular damage.  Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
